---
title: Smoky Mushroom Quesadillas with Oven-Baked Wedges, Pickled Onion and Baby Leaf Salad
description: Sandwiched together with a savoury mushroom filling plus plenty of cheese, these Smoky Mushroom Quesadillas are a Mexican inspired favourite laden with smoky flavour.
